&lt;li&gt;Guide clients in appropriately selecting and maximizing the value of integrated, disparate data sources&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a trusted thought leader by providing strategic insights and recommendations beyond transactional data procurement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate clients by hosting post-sale training sessions to impart your expertise and recommendations on the effective use of healthcare data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer forward-thinking guidance on emerging data trends, novel analytic approaches, and best practices in real-world evidence generation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and deliver study specific presentations, data feasibility assessments and proposals in the pre-sales phase&lt;/li&gt;
