&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How you will help&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;HealthVerity’s Partners vertical develops strategic and commercial relationships with industry-leading and early-stage consulting, analytics, and technology firms that serve life sciences and healthcare clients across the value chain (R&amp;amp;D, RWE, commercial). Essentially, any organization that is not a biopharmaceutical company, government agency, or payer falls under our remit.&lt;/p&gt;
