&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About HealthVerity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;HealthVerity is the leading infrastructure provider for identity, privacy, governance, and data exchange to pharma, insurers, and government. Our platform manages 250+ billion HIPAA-compliant transactions across 340 million Americans, with privacy-protecting identity resolution that is 10x more accurate than traditional methods, and is deployed at 250+ major pharma, insurance, and data ecosystem partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In May 2026, HealthVerity completed the acquisition of Symphony Health from ICON plc — bringing together HealthVerity&#39;s Marketplace and Identity Manager infrastructure with Symphony Health&#39;s 40+ years of leadership in pharma commercial data and analytics, including its Integrated Dataverse (IDV®) open claims platform, Synoma® tokenization engine, PatientSource® longitudinal data, and a brand analytics, targeting, and managed markets portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The combined company spans the end-to-end pharma life cycle — R&amp;amp;D, RWE/HEOR, government, partners, media, and commercial T&amp;amp;C and BA — with 200M+ active 2-year patient coverage in closed claims, 125M+ active patient coverage via EMR, 90% retail pharmacy Rx coverage, 67% specialty drug activity, and 7 of the top 10 closed claims suppliers. Together, we are defining the next era of healthcare data: best-in-class quality and coverage, modern infrastructure, and relentless innovation on patient insights in the highest-growth markets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring our SVP, Product to lead the strategy, vision, and execution of the entire product portfolio for the combined company. As a member of the executive leadership team reporting directly to the CEO, the SVP, Product will own the long-term direction of how HealthVerity transforms data, analytics, and AI capabilities into differentiated, durable, market-leading products across client segments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a defining role at a defining moment. The healthcare data market is being reshaped: clients are squeezing budgets and demanding broader, more clinical insights; data source transparency is increasing; and AI is fundamentally changing how insights are produced, delivered, and consumed — collapsing traditional cost structures and creating new opportunities for differentiated value. The combined HealthVerity + Symphony Health platform is uniquely positioned to lead this transition — and the SVP, Product will be the leader who defines what we build, how we monetize it, and how we use AI to move from data sales into higher-margin, differentiated software-and-services offerings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This leader will serve as a true partner to the CEO and executive team — helping to shape our commercial strategy, capital allocation, M&amp;amp;A, and go-to-market direction alongside owning product strategy and execution with the goal of driving growth and industry differentiation.&lt;/p&gt;
